20. Add tests, docs, runbooks, and acceptance gates

IMPORTANT SAFETY RULES:
- Do not enable live trading by default.
- Do not enable real IoT actions by default.
- Do not enable real social posting by default.
- Do not bypass Guardian risk checks.
- Do not bypass content approval checks.
- Do not bypass tenant isolation.
- Do not bypass billing entitlements.
- Do not bypass governance policies.
- Do not bypass final GA safety gates.
- Do not bypass data residency enforcement.
- AI Boardroom outputs are decision-support only, not automatic execution.
- Strategic recommendations must be advisory by default.
- Capital allocation simulation is educational/planning only, not financial advice.
- Legal/compliance outputs are operational templates only, not legal advice.
- Market/competitor intelligence must store source summaries and confidence levels.
- No automated outreach, billing changes, trading actions, hiring/firing actions, legal actions, or public announcements may run automatically.
- No secrets, credentials, tokens, broker credentials, private customer payloads, raw prompts, API keys, or confidential documents may be logged, exported, synced, or displayed.
- All recommendations must include assumptions, confidence, evidence summary, risks, and limitations.

