============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

AI_BOARDROOM_ENABLED=true
AI_BOARDROOM_MODE=advisory
AI_BOARDROOM_DRY_RUN=true
AI_BOARDROOM_REQUIRE_HUMAN_APPROVAL=true
AI_BOARDROOM_MAX_DEBATE_TURNS=12

STRATEGY_ENGINE_ENABLED=true
STRATEGY_RECOMMENDATIONS_ADVISORY=true
STRATEGY_REQUIRE_APPROVAL=true

OKR_ENGINE_ENABLED=true
INITIATIVE_SCORING_ENABLED=true
ROADMAP_PLANNING_ENABLED=true

SCENARIO_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true
SCENARIO_SIMULATION_DRY_RUN=true
SCENARIO_MAX_RUNS_PER_REQUEST=10

ECOSYSTEM_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true
ECOSYSTEM_SIMULATION_DRY_RUN=true

CAPITAL_ALLOCATION_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true
CAPITAL_ALLOCATION_DRY_RUN=true
CAPITAL_ALLOCATION_NOT_FINANCIAL_ADVICE=true

INTELLIGENCE_ENABLED=true
MARKET_INTELLIGENCE_ENABLED=true
COMPETITIVE_INTELLIGENCE_ENABLED=true
INTELLIGENCE_REQUIRE_EVIDENCE=true
INTELLIGENCE_MIN_CONFIDENCE=0.60
INTELLIGENCE_STORE_RAW_SOURCES=false

DECISION_MEMOS_ENABLED=true
BOARD_MEETING_AUTOMATION_ENABLED=true
BOARD_VOTING_ENABLED=true

Rules:
- AI Boardroom must be advisory by default.
- Boardroom must never directly execute operational changes.
- Strategy recommendations must require human approval before any action.
- Scenario simulation must be dry-run only.
- Capital allocation outputs must include planning-only disclaimer.
- Intelligence outputs must include evidence and confidence.
- Raw sources must not be stored unless explicitly configured.
- No secrets or confidential payloads may be included in memos, minutes, reports, or simulations.

