backend/app/boardroom/board_audit.py

BoardAgentsService methods:
- register_default_board_agents()
- list_agents()
- get_agent(role)
- update_agent(role, patch)
- disable_agent(role)

Default board agents:
- CEO: strategy, priorities, execution clarity
- COO: operating model, process, delivery risk
- CFO: unit economics, budget, runway, cost control
- CTO: architecture, scalability, technical feasibility
- CISO: security, risk, compliance, data protection
- CRO: revenue, sales, GTM, customer pipeline
- CMO: positioning, growth, brand, demand generation
- General Counsel advisor: legal/commercial template warnings only
- Investor advisor: fundraising and investor-readiness simulation only
- Customer advocate: usability, trust, customer outcomes

DebateEngine methods:
- start_debate(topic, prompt, participants)
- generate_agent_position(agent, context)
- run_debate(session_id)
- summarize_debate(session_id)
- extract_recommendations(session_id)

Rules:
- Debate outputs are advisory.
- Every recommendation includes assumptions, risks, confidence, and limitations.
- No debate output may execute actions.
- No legal/financial advice claims.

BoardVoteService methods:
- create_vote(session_id, role, vote, rationale)
- tally_votes(session_id)
- create_decision_from_vote(session_id)

MeetingService methods:
- create_agenda(topic, context)
- generate_minutes(meeting_id)
- list_meetings()
- get_meeting(meeting_id)

DecisionMemoService methods:
- create_memo(request)
- generate_memo_from_debate(session_id)
- list_memos()
- get_memo(memo_id)
- update_status(memo_id, status)

BoardAudit methods:
- record_board_event()
- list_board_audit()
- export_board_audit()

