GET /api/intelligence/reports/{report_id}/markdown

Rules:
- Auth required.
- Tenant scoped.
- Standard response shape required.
- Advisory by default.
- All reports must include confidence and limitations.
- No endpoint may execute operational changes automatically.
- No endpoint may expose secrets or raw confidential payloads.

