============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- BOARDROOM_DISABLED
- BOARD_AGENT_NOT_FOUND
- BOARD_DEBATE_NOT_FOUND
- BOARD_DECISION_NOT_FOUND
- DECISION_MEMO_NOT_FOUND
- STRATEGY_ENGINE_DISABLED
- OBJECTIVE_NOT_FOUND
- KEY_RESULT_NOT_FOUND
- INITIATIVE_NOT_FOUND
- ROADMAP_ITEM_NOT_FOUND
- SCENARIO_SIMULATION_FAILED
- ECOSYSTEM_SIMULATION_FAILED
- STRATEGIC_RISK_NOT_FOUND
- CAPITAL_ALLOCATION_DISABLED
- INTELLIGENCE_DISABLED
- EVIDENCE_NOT_FOUND
- INTELLIGENCE_LOW_CONFIDENCE
- COMPETITOR_NOT_FOUND
- INTELLIGENCE_REPORT_NOT_FOUND
- ADVISORY_ONLY_ACTION
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

